653139-le-recyclage-des-éléments-poubelles-sacs-poubelle-industrie-de-la-gestion-des-pneus-utilisent-les-déchet-1-1300x994-1.jpg 1300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" />											\n										<img width=\"765\" height=\"543\" src=\"http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/obama-clean-energy-standard-dependence-oil_303.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/obama-clean-energy-standard-dependence-oil_303.jpg 765w, http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/obama-clean-energy-standard-dependence-oil_303-300x213.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 765px) 100vw, 765px\" />											\n										<img width=\"717\" height=\"536\" src=\"http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/food.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/food.jpg 717w, http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/food-300x224.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 717px) 100vw, 717px\" />											\n										<img width=\"468\" height=\"390\" src=\"http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/fier.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/fier.jpg 468w, http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/fier-300x250.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 468px) 100vw, 468px\" />											\n		<p>Tu es déjà très prometteur si tu lis toujours!<br />Ta planète croit en toi.</p><p>Si jamais tu as des questions ou besoin de support,<br />contacte-nous via <a href=\"aide.html\">Aide </a>!<br />On se tient à ta disposition dès que tu en as besoin !</p>		\n										<img width=\"394\" height=\"338\" src=\"http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/unnamed.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/unnamed.jpg 394w, http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/unnamed-300x257.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 394px) 100vw, 394px\" />", "Accueil", "", "inherit", "closed", "closed", "", "24-revision-v1", 